    <div class="field field-name-field-teaser field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Any content-staging workflow is going to have conflicts. In the simplest form a conflict exists when trying to import content that already exists. In more complex cases conflict might occur between revisions.</p>
<p>Having a solid API to detect and handle conflicts is key to any content-staging workflow. Read on to find out how Entity Pilot handles conflicts via an extendable plugin system.</p>
